<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>Hi <%= @user.first_name %>,</h2>
    <p>
      This is a remainder mail as you have applied for <%= link_to @position.employer, user_position_url(@user, @position) %> which is going to get closed on <%= @position.close_date.strftime("%e %b %Y") %>. You have applied for this job on <%= @position.applied_date.strftime("%e %b %Y") %>
      <% unless @position.interview_date.blank? %>
        and gave an interview on <%= @position.interview_date.strftime("%e %b %Y") %>
      <% end %>
    </p>
    <br>
    <p>Cheers,</p>
    <p>- Job Applicaiton Tracker App Team.</p>
  </body>
</html>
